The paper deals with texture image retrieval using deep learning and hashing techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The use of deep learning architectures and attention mechanisms also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval techniques for image databases, which could also place it under the information retrieval (cs.IR) category.
